 Lek8-tek-kou kong2, Goa2 long2 oe7 ka3 li2, goa2 tui3 soe3-han3 choe3 koaiN3-si3 lah, chit tiap8 iau2-ku2 ki3-tit, li2 beh oh8 mah? Goa2 in3 i kong2, Oh8 hit e5, beh-thai2 u7 thang thak8 chheh nih8, goa2 na7 u7 am3-thau5 chit8 tiap8-a2 ku2 eng5, thang lai5 thak8 chheh, pat8 si5 goan2 lau7-bu2 m7 chun2 goa2 lai5. 
 Kho-ni2 kong2, Goa2 oh8 hit e5, thang a2 m7 thang? thak8 chheh si7 khah bo5 iau3-kin2, in-ui7 goa2 chin7 tun7. Lek8-tek-kou kong2, KhoaN3 li2 hit ki chhiu2 hiah chhou-lou2, ia7 m7 ho2 so soh-a2. Koh ka7 goa2 kong2, Li2 thak8 te7 ji7 chat. Goa2 chiu7 thak8, hit si5 sim-lai7 long2 bo5 siuN7 ji7, in-ui7 goa2 su-sim beh choe3 e5, kap chai tioh8 choe3 e5, nng7 ho7 e5 liam7-thau5, chhap-chhap ju5 ti7 sim-lai7. Kho-ni2 chiu7 un5-un5-a2 teh thak8 hit e5 te7 saN chat kong2, “Ki-tok bo5 kiu5 ka-ki7 e5 hoaN-hi2.” Goa2 thiaN chit chat chheh, ti7 sim-lai7 na2 si7 teh tui3 goa2 kong2 e5, goa2 thak8 liau2, chiu7 chu2-i3 tiaN7-tioh8 beh oh8 so soh-a2, ka7 Lek8-tek-kou kong2, ChhiaN2 li2 ka3 goa2 an3-choaN2 so. I kong2, Li2 an2-ni chiah si7 ho2 gin2-a2, li2 tiam3 hia oh8 so, goa2 tiam3 chia ka3 Kho-ni2 thak8, kau3 li2 oe7 so, i iah8 oe7 thak8. Hia u7 koa2 ta chhau2-a2, li2 theh8-lai5, goa2 ka3 li2 so, chi2 kui2 jit8 Kho-ni2 tioh8 koah koa2 chhau2-a2, ka7 Pi2-tek pi7-pan7 he7-teh. Kho-ni2 kong2, An2-ni chin7 ho2, goa2 ka7 i pi7-pan7. 
 Goan2 chiu7 to3-khi3 goan2 tau. Lun7 hit e5 so soh-a2 chin7 koe7 oh8, koh goa2 ia7 ai3 so, oh8 chit8 le2-pai3 ku2, hit e5 Lek8-tek-kou khoaN3 liau2 chiu7 kong2, Li2 oe7 hiau2-tit so lah, thang khi3 ka3 Pi2-tek. 
 Goan2 hit jit8 to3-lai5 e5 si5, Kho-ni2 chiu7 koah chit8 khun2 chhau2-a2, goa2 theh8 sou2 so e5 soh-a2, beh to3-khi3 hou7 Pi2-tek khoaN3, hou7 i chai goa2 oe7 hiau2-tit so, ia7 so chin7 ho2. KiaN5 beh kau3 goan2 tau, khoaN3-kiN3 Pi2-tek iu5-goan5 to2 ti7 hi2 soa-nih8, goa2 chiu7 chau2 kau3 hia kong2, Pi2-tek, goa2 ka7 li2 kong2 chit8 hang7 tai7-chi3, goa2 beh ka3 li2 so soh-a2; hit e5 Lek8-tek-kou kong2 goa2 si7 iong2-kiaN7 e5, li2 si7 loan2-jiok8 e5, goa2 eng-kai pang-chan7 li2. Goa2 i2-keng oh8 oe7 hiau2-tit so lah, beh lai5 ka3 li2. 
 Pi2-tek bin7 choe3 i oat8-khi3 bo5 beh khoaN3, goa2 chai i bo5 sim2-mih8 hoaN-hi2, chiu7 khoeh i hia che7, kong2, Li2 m7 sai2 siu7-khi3, tu2-a2 chiah teh kong2 li2 loan2-jiok8 e5, si7 kong2 li2 tak8 jit8 tiaN7-tiaN7 toa3 chia, boe7-oe7 thang khi3 thit-tho5, bo5 chhin-chhiuN7 goan2 thang khi3 siaN5-nih8, he kiam2 bo5 ut-ut chut-chut mah? I thiaN liau2 iau2-ku2 bin7 choe3 i oat8-teh. Goa2 koh kong2, Kho-ni2 lian5 goa2 kap hit e5 Lek8-tek-kou, long2 siuN7 li2 tek-khak beh oh8 so soh-a2, goa2 u7 toa3 chit8 tiau5 pan7 lai5, li2 siaN2-su7 m7 khoaN3-khoaN3 cheh? Kho-ni2 ka7 li2 koah hiah choe7 chhau2-a2 hiahN lai5. 
 Pi2-tek iau2-bo5 beh chhiu3-chhai2, ia7 bo5 beh khoaN3, choe3 i teh so chhiu2, chhin-chhiuN7 chin kan-khou2. Bo5 loa7 ku2 i chiu7 eng7 chhiu2 ng bin7 khau3-khi2-lai5. Goa2 kong2, Li2 m7 sai2 khau3, m7 sai2 khau3. I kong2, Goa2 chin iu-bun7 ah; goa2 si7 bo5 lou7-eng7 e5 lang5, chit8-si3-lang5 si7 an2-ni lah, goa2 siuN7 Kho-ni2 ti7 hi2 chhu3 nih8, lau7-bu2 bin7-thau5-cheng5 sui-jian5 u7 hiam5 i, m7 ku2 ka-chiah-au7 teh o-lo2 i si7 chin ho2 e5 gin2-a2, si7 chit ke sou2 oa2-kho3 e5. Chhin-chhiuN7 li2 si7 cha-bou2 e5, m7 ku2 oe7 bang7 he5, ia7 oe7 thak8 chheh, goa2 si7 boe7 choe3 poaN3 hang7, ia7 long2 boe7 hiau2-tit sim2-mih8 tai7-chi3 e5 lang5. SiuN7 se3-kan siaN2-su7 siN goa2 che bo5 lou7-eng7 e5 lang5? I na2 kong2 na2 khau3, khau3 kau3 sau siaN, goa2 chiu7 chin kiaN, in-ui7 i eng2 si5 long2 m7-bat khau3 kau3 an2-ni, i ia7 eng2 m7-bat kong2 ka-ki7 e5 tai7-chi3. TaN an2-ni kong2, chiu7 bo5 hoat thang an-ui3 i, na7 u7 che7 ti7 i sin-piN, thiaN i koh kong2 sim2-mih8 oe7. Tiap8-a2 ku2 i koh kong2, Eng2 siong5-si5 li2 kap Kho-ni2 choe3-tui, sin7 goa2 ka-ki7 chit8 e5, taN li2 beh ka3 goa2 choe3 chit e5, si7 siaN2-su7 nih? phah-sng3 li2 kap Kho-ni2 long2 bo5 beh chhap goa2. 
 Goa2 kong2, Goa2 long2 m7 chai li2 u7 an2-ni siuN7, Kho-ni2 i ia7 m7 chai; li2 boh8-tit an2-ni siuN7, li2 thang kap goa2 oh8 so soh-a2, li2 na7 oh8 oe7 hiau2-tit chiu7 thang choe3 u7 lou7-eng7 e5 lang5. Che soh-a2 na7 khi3 boe7, oe7 tat8 choe7-choe7 chiN5. Chit tiap8 lang5 long2 koaN2-kin2 teh siu-li2 chhu3, soh-a2 si7 choe3 chhu3-teng2 e5 lou7-eng7, ke-ke hou7-hou7 long2 tioh8 eng7. Li2 na7 so soh-a2, oe7 hou7 lau7-bu2 hoaN-hi2, kiam2 m7 si7 u7 lou7-eng7 e5 lang5 mah? 
 I thiaN chiah-e5 oe7, chiu7 na2 bo5 khau3, chiong i e5 chhiu2 tui3 bin7-nih pang3-loh8-khi3, khoaN3 goa2 sou2 so e5 soh-a2. Kho-ni2 ia7 ka7 i hiahN chhau2-a2 lai5. Pi2-tek khoaN3-kiN3 chiu7 chin7 hoaN-hi2, beh tai7-seng so chit8 tiau5 chat-a2 khoaN3 oe7 sai2-tit a2 boe7 sai2-tit. Goan2 saN lang5 tiaN7-tioh8 chu2-i3, chiong so soh-a2 e5 tai7-chi3, bo5 beh hou7 goan2 lau7-bu2 chai, chiu7 ti7 li7-khui ke bo5 hng7 khi3 so soh-a2. Goan2 lau7-bu2 tak8 jit8 bo5 eng5, teh koaN2 choe3 kang, ia7 bo5 chhap goan2. Pi2-tek so chit8 tiau5, chiu7 khoan5 khi2-lai5, Kho-ni2 ka7 i theh8-khi3 siu phoa3 chun5 lai7. Che chun5 si7 peng2-phak khoa3 ti7 hai2-kiN5. Theng3-hau7 i so kau3 choe7-choe7, chiah khi3 boe7 chiN5, hou7 lau7-bu2. 
 Kho-ni2 ka7 i kong2, Goa2 ka7 li2 chhong3 choe7-choe7 chhau2-a2, khoaN3 li2 kau3 loa7 gau5 so, long2 hu3 chiok li2 eng7. Goa2 in-ui7 tai7-seng bo5 kap Kho-ni2 iau3-kin2 Pi2-tek e5 su7, taN khioh u7 teh hoan2-hoe2. Hit chit8 am3 to ia7 chin hoaN-hi2, kau3 to2-teh khun3 e5 si5, goa2 am3-chiN7 teh ka-ki7 siuN7, Ia5-sou chai Pi2-tek oe7 oh8 an2-ni choe3, ia7 tek-khak hoaN-hi2. 
 Te7 lak8 chiuN 
 Kau3 poeh geh8, tiong-chhiu chiu7 kin2 kau3, siuN7 liau2-au7 jit8 te2, chin koe7 am3, am3-thau5 chin7 oe7 bo5 eng5, kiaN-liau2-boe7-oe7 thak8 khah choe7, phah-sng3 tioh8 pat8 si5 chiah oe7 kap hit e5 Lek8-tek-kou thak8, in-ui7 goa2 na2 siuN7, sim-lai7 na2 tioh8-kip, ai3 kau3 boe7-tit chit8 si5 kin2-me2 oe7. 
 U7 chit8 jit8 khi3 mng7 Lek8-tek-kou kong2, Tak8 le2-pai3-jit8 cha2-khi2, goa2 ia7 lai5 thak8, ho2 a2 m7? I kong2, Thang lai5, chong2-si7 hit jit8 goa2 bo5 ti7-teh. Goa2 kong2, Le2-pai3-jit8 cha2-khi2 li2 ta2-loh8 khi3 nih? I kong2, Khi3 le2-pai3-tng5. Goa2 chiu7 houN3 chit8 siaN kong2, To bo5 khoaN3 li2 u7 sim2-mih8 ho2 saN, chheng-chheng khoaN3-kiN3 li2 chi2 piah-teng2 kui3 chit8 teng2 chhiN2 bo7-a2 na7-tiaN7. I chiu7 chhio3 kong2, Ho2 i-chiuN5 khiok ki5 bo5, che bo7-a2 ti3 u7 chap8 sou3 ni5 lah. 
 Goa2 kong2, Chit teng2 bo7-a2 si7 oe7 ti3-tit, na7-si7 ti3 khi3 le2-pai3-tng5 chiu7 boe7 choe3-tit. I kong2, SiaN2-su7 boe7 choe3-tit? thiaN li2 an2-ni kong2, chiu7 chai li2 be7 bat khi3 le2-pai3-tng5. Goa2 kong2, U7 khi3 lah, chong2-si7 put-ko3 tiam3 ti7 hi2 mng5-khau2, bo5 jip8-khi3 lai7-bin7, khoaN3 hiah-e5 jip8-khi3 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5, long2 si7 chheng7 tiu5-toan7, ti3 sui2 bo7 koa3 chhah khong2-chhiok mng5, long2 bo5 lang5 ti3 chhin-chhiuN7 li2 chit teng2 chhiN2 bo7-a2. I kong2, He2 si7 ta2-loh8 chit8 keng e5? Goa2 kong2, Chiu7-si7 siaN5-lai7 sin khi2 e5. I kong2, Hit keng lang5 si7 ti7 siaN5-lai7 tiau5-kou3-i3 khi2 beh hou7 chhut-goa7 lang5 le2-pai3 e5, in gim5 si ki5-to2, long2 eng7 Eng-kok oe7. Goan2 peng5-siong5 lang5 chiu7 bo5 khi3 hia, si7 in-ui7 beh thiaN goan2 e5 thou2-im, chiah siong5-siong5 khi3 kap goan2 saN-kun7 hit keng e5 le2-pai3-tng5. Chit keng si7 kong2 Ui-li7-su7 oe7 e5, li2 na7 kap goa2 khi3, chiu7 oe7 khoaN3-kiN3 choe7-choe7 ti3 chhin-chhiuN7 goa2 ti3 chit ho7 chhiN2 bo7-a2 e5; e7 le2-pai3-jit8 li2 tioh8 kap goa2 khi3. 
 Goa2 kong2, Lang5 khi3 hi2 le2-pai3-tng5 si7 choe3 sim2-mih8? I chiu7 khi2 iu-bun7 e5 khoan2, liong7-iok i ka-ki7 teh siuN7 gin2-a2 kau3 chiah toa7-han3, iau2-boe7 hiau2-tit khi3 le2-pai3-tng5 si7 choe3 sim2-mih8. Lek8-tek-kou chiu7 kong2, EN-a2, goan2 khi3 le2-pai3-tng5, chiu7-si7 beh ki5-to2 Chu2, o-lo2 Chu2, ia7 beh thiaN Chu2 e5 Seng3-keng, kap lang5 teh khui-thiah Seng3-keng e5 to7-li2. 
 Goa2 kong2, Na7-si7 u7 ki5-to2, goa2 chiu7 beh khi3, in-ui7 goa2 siong5-siong5 kiaN boe7 hiau2 ki5-to2. Cha2-cheng5 u7 chit8 ui7 thai3-thai3 ka7 goa2 kong2 tioh8 ki5-to2, goa2 tiaN7-tiaN7 iu-bun7 bo5 lang5 ka3 goa2, li2 na7 chhoa7 goa2 khi3, goa2 chin ai3 khi3 lah. Hit si5 sim-lai7 ai3 kau3 boe7 kou3-tit thang liam5-piN kau3 le2-pai3-jit8. 
 Kau3 pai3-lak8 e5-hng, chiu7 long2 boe7 khun3-tit, ai3 thiN kin2-me2 kng. Kau3 thiN chhim2-chhim2-a2 kng, goan2 lau7-bu2 khun3 iau2-be7 chhiN2, siuN7-tioh8 hit e5 Lek8-tek-kou bat kong2, put-koan2 chheng7 sim2-mih8 saN khi3, long2 thang. Sou2-i2 bo5 theng3-hau7 ka7 goan2 lau7-bu2 hiahN sin saN, chiu7 chheng7 pun2 teh chheng7 e5 saN, thng3 chhiah kha, khi3 chhe7 Lek8-tek-kou. Chit8 e7 jip8 mng5 i khoaN3-kiN3 goa2, chiu7 u7 lioh8-a2 ki5-koai3, ia7 bo5 kap goa2 kong2 sim2-mih8. 
 ThiaN-kiN3 le2-pai3-tng5 teh kong3 cheng, goan2 chiu7 khi2-sin khi3. Jip8 le2-pai3-tng5 iau2-be7 u7 lang5 lai5, goa2 khoaN3 goa2 ka-ki7 e5 saN kiaN-lang5, chiu7 chin7 kian3-siau3. Tu2-a2 kap Lek8-tek-kou ti7 hia teh che7, hut-jian5 thiaN-kiN3 u7 hiah choe7 kha-pou7 siaN, oat8-thau5 chit8 e7 ka7 i khoaN3-cheh, u7 hiah choe7 e5 gin2-a2 chit8 tui3 chit8 tui3 saN-khan chhiu2 jip8-lai5, sim-lai7 chin ki5-koai3, siuN7 chiah-e5 gin2-a2, long2 beh lai5 choe3 sim2-mih8. Bo5 loa7 ku2, bok8-su chiu7 chiuN7 tai5, thak8 Seng3-chheh, khui-thiah to7-li2. Hit jit8 ti7 le2-pai3-tng5 u7 choe7-choe7 goa2 thiaN boe7 hiau2-tit, chong2-si7 hong2-hut na2 u7 chit8 ui7, goan2 khoaN3 boe7 kiN3 e5 ti7 hia thiaN goan2 sou2 kiu5. Cha2 goa2 ti7 hit soa-khut-nih8 ki5-to2, bo5 an2-ni, put-ko3 sin3 Ia5-sou beh thiaN goa2 na7-tiaN7. Lek8-tek-kou ka7 goa2 kong2, TaN ti7 chi2 le2-pai3-tng5 nih8, chiu7 chai Ia5-sou u7 kap lan2 ti7-teh. Goan2 ki5-to2 liau2, chiu7 gim5 chit8 siu2 si, bok8-su koh teh kong2 to7-li2, goa2 che7 kau3 chit tiap8, chiu7 ia3-sian7, sim chin ai3 thiaN, m7 ku2 chin sian7, chiu7 thau5-khak tuh ti7 Lek8-tek-kou e5 keng-thau5 piN teh khun3, kau3 lang5 beh kui7-loh8-khi3 ki5-to2, goa2 chiah chhiN2. Kau3 le2-pai3 soah, chiu7 kap Lek8-tek-kou to3-lai5, chit8 lou7 ia7 bo5 kong2 sim2-mih8 oe7. 
 Bin5-a2 e5-hng, goa2 khi3 thak8 chheh e5 si5, mng7 i kong2, Le2-pai3-tng5 nih8 hiah-e5 gin2-a2 teh chhong3 sim2-mih8? I kong2, In si7 oh8 Seng3-keng Hoe7 e5 hak8-seng, kap in sian-siN thak8, choe3 chit8 e7 khi3 le2-pai3-tng5 thak8 Seng3-chheh, thak8 si, oh8 gim5 si. Goa2 kong2, Put-lun7 chhin3-chhai2 e5 gin2-a2 long2 thang khi3 mah? I kong2, Li2 na7 ai3 khi3, na7 lin2 lau7-bu2 beh hou7 li2 khi3, he si7 chin ho2. Goa2 kong2, Goa2 chin ai3 khi3 lah, theng3-hau7 goa2 to3-lai5 khi3 mng7 goan2 lau7-bu2, i na7 beh hou7 goa2 khi3, goa2 chiu7 khi3. 
 Chheh thak8 liau2 chiu7 kin2-me2 to3-khi3, beh mng7 goan2 lau7-bu2 chun2 goa2 khi3 Seng3-keng Hoe7 thak8 mah. Sim-lai7 ka-ki7 teh phah-sng3 i tek-khak chun2 goa2 khi3. Chit8 e7 jip8 mng5, ia7 bo5 koan2 i chhu3-lai7 u7 sim2-mih8 tai7-chi3, tit8-tit8 chau2-kau3 goan2 lau7-bu2 bin7-cheng5 kong2, Li2 beh hou7 goa2 chheng7 hit nia2 chui2-ang5 saN, khi3 Seng3-keng Hoe7 thak8 mah? I chiu7 soa3 siu7-khi3 kong2, Hit e5 khi3 oh8 Seng3-keng Hoe7, goa2 long2 m7 chun2 li2, li2 beh oh8 chit e5, oh8 hit e5, chiong-lai5 soa3 bo5 chit8 e5 thang saN-pang, li2 khoaN3 hiah-e5 mi7-pau teh, chi7-chui7 beh chiah8 ah? Goa2 thiaN-kiN3 kong2, chiu7 oa2 khi3 toh-teng2 chit8 e7 khoaN3, khoaN3-kiN3 kui2 e5 mi7-pau, long2 pek kau3 chhau3-ta toh8-he2, ou ma-ma, chha-put-to long2 boe7 chiah8 tit. Goan2 lau7-bu2 koh kong2, Che long2 si7 in-ui7 lin2 thak8 chheh sou2 ti3 e5. Au7-lai5 goa2 tek-khak lun2 boe7 tiau5, chhut-chai7 lin2 lah. 
